Package com.regula.documentreader.api.enums

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocReaderAction
    Contains all possible DocumentReaderNotification callback codes
    DocReaderScenario
    Contains all possible values of ProcessParam.scenario
    eCheckResult
    Contains all possible of field validity check
    eGraphicFieldType
    Class, contains fields, describing all possible types of document's graphic fields (portrait, signature etc.)
    eImageQualityCheckType
    Contains all possible values of Image Quality Check result
    eRFID_AccessControl_ProcedureType
    contains a set of constants that define the type of authentication or secure data access procedure
    eRFID_AuthenticationProcedureType
    contains a set of constants that define the type of performed procedure of document authentication within the context of the communication session with electronic document
    eRFID_BaudRate
    contains a set of constants specifying the rate of data ex-change between the reader and the RFID-chip
    eRFID_CertificateType
    contains a set of constants that define the type of certificate used in the procedure of document security object digital signature verification
    eRFID_DataFile_Type
    contains a set of constants that define the file type (or logical belonging of the data object) within the context of the communication session with electronic document
    eRFID_ErrorCodes
    contains a set of error codes returned by the MCL func-tions or transferred to the user application by the callback-function.
    eRFID_NotificationCodes
    contains a set of notification codes trans-ferred to the user application by calling the callback-function
    eRFID_Password_Type
    contains a set of constants that define the type of key to access the protected data
    eRFID_ResultType
    contains a set of constants specifying the type of data stored in TResultContainer container structure
    eRFID_SDK_ProfilerType
    SDK LDS data profiler type
    eRFID_TerminalType
    contains a set of constants that define the type of terminal within the context of the communication session with electronic document
    eRPRM_FieldVerificationResult
    Class, contains fields, describing all possible validation codes for lexical analysis
    eRPRM_ResultType
    contains a pool of constants which determine the type of data stored in the TResultContainer container structure.
    eRPRM_SecurityFeatureType
    contains identifiers determining types of elements for a document authenticity checking.
    eSignManagementAction  
    eVisualFieldType
    contains identifiers determining the logical type of the text data obtained while reading MRZ, document filling fields and bar-codes.
    LCID
    contains possible ID of language-culture to differentiate one field of the same type from another (for example Belarus Passport Page # 31 – Belarusian and Russian fields of the same type)
